tools.description:
Tool to process whole supplier flow
## WHAT IT DOES
Processes supplier workflow stages - recommendations, validations, and supplier management.

## WHEN TO CALL
Call this tool at each supplier workflow step with the appropriate supplierStage.

Keep the payload in "data" parameter which is of the type object

Correct example for "data" parameter
```json 
{
"data": {
	"supplierStage": "getNonSelectedSupplier",
	"pageSize": 6,
	"invokedForSupplierCards": true,
	"selectedRecommendedSuppliers": [
		{
			"legalCompanyName": "International Vending Management, Inc.",
			"partnerCode": "624aad1c-c013-4db7-af35-d64ad3c6ebd5"
		},
		{
			"legalCompanyName": "Provizer Solutions",
			"partnerCode": "a8949c23-ce11-4a0d-bcd8-b697b9998e48"
		}
	],
	"userEnteredSupplier": [
		"TCS",
		"GEP",
		"LNT",
		"ABC"
	],
	"selectedUserEnteredSuppliers": [
		{
			"legalCompanyName": "ABC",
			"partnerCode": "ab09c8e2-c487-41ca-a6dd-03a9f478e5f0",
			"similarTo": "ABC"
		}
	],
	"newSuppliers": []
}
}
```
